# Change Safety Rule

## Purpose
Favor minimal, safe, reversible change.

## Requirements
- prefer scoped edits over broad rewrites
- call out contract-breaking changes
- identify migration impacts before structural edits
- preserve backward compatibility unless explicitly changing it
- separate speculative improvements from required fixes

## Apply When
- editing existing code
- changing contracts, schemas, or deployment configuration
- proposing refactors
- fixing bugs in shared systems
